posts.title: Introduction
posts.text: Self IntroI am currently a second-year EE major at Washington University in St. Louis, expecting to graduate in January 2023.Looking for a full-time job in software development. During school, I took courses related to software development ,such as web development, advanced algorithms, machine learning, and mobile application development. In my previous internship, I was exposed to some mainstream front-end and back-end frameworks and the use of databases. This summer, I developed a cross-platform robot navigation project based on SLAM, and controlled the robot through an Android application.

posts.title: Hello World
posts.text: Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub. Quick StartCreate a new post1$ hexo new "My New Post" More info: Writing Run server1$ hexo server More info: Server Generate static files1$ hexo generate More info: Generating Deploy to remote sites1$ hexo deploy More info: Deployment
